Any Issue that have been made aware to me have been listed here: [Issue Tracker] (https://github.com/Robert12905/Personal-Website---myHTML/issues)

To ensure the website remains professional and maintainable, all contributions should strive to follow these industry-standard style guides:
  HTML/CSS: Google HTML/CSS Style Guide
  JavaScript: Airbnb JavaScript Style Guide
  Accessibility: All images must include meaningful alt text, and the site should remain navigable via keyboard.
  Language: Documentation and code comments must be provided in English.

By contributing to this repository, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under the project's MIT license.

